title: Romania off to rough start at world gymnastics championships
text:
> Sports Romania off to rough start at world gymnastics championships Romania's Larisa Iordache performs during her beam routine as she takes part in the women's qualification competition at the World Artistic Gymnastics championships in Glasgow, Scotland, Friday, Oct. 23, 2015.
